---
import MainHead from '../../components/MainHead.astro'

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<MainHead
			title="Priisma - Privacy policy"
			description="Priisma Privacy policy"
		/>
	</head>
	<body class=" bg-slate-100 text-slate-800">
		<header class="px-4 py-4 mx-auto mt-8 sm:px-6 md:max-w-2xl md:px-4 lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-12">
			<h1 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="mb-8 text-sm text-slate-600">Last updated: 05/02/2023</p>
		</header>
		<section class="px-4 pb-12 mx-auto sm:px-6 md:max-w-2xl md:px-4 lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-12">

			<p>At ReCraft, your privacy is of utmost importance to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect the personal information we receive through LinkedIn Lead Gen Forms ("Form Data"). By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.</p>

			<h2 class="my-4 font-bold text-md">Collection and Use of Form Data</h2>
			<p>We collect and use Form Data submitted by registered LinkedIn members through Lead Gen Forms on Pages, subject to the privacy policy linked to the Lead Gen Forms, applicable laws, and the scope of consents obtained through the Lead Gen Forms. We use this information to: (a) provide our services, (b) communicate with you, and (c) improve and enhance our services.</p>
			
			<h2 class="my-4 font-bold text-md">Sharing of Form Data</h2>
			<p>We may share Form Data with third parties acting on our behalf, such as service providers, to help us provide our services. We are responsible for ensuring their compliance with these Service Terms and for limiting their use of Form Data on our behalf. We do not sell Form Data under any circumstances.</p>
			
			<h2 class="my-4 font-bold text-md">Legal and Unlawful Use</h2>
			<p>We will not use Form Data in any unlawful manner (e.g., unlawful discrimination). We will comply with all applicable laws and regulations when handling Form Data.</p>
			
			<h2 class="my-4 font-bold text-md">Opt-Out and Deletion Requests</h2>
			<p>If a LinkedIn member requests to opt-out of our communications or have his or her Form Data deleted, we will honor such request promptly.</p>
			
			<h2 class="my-4 font-bold text-md">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
			<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Effective Date" at the top of this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.</p>
			
			<h2 class="my-4 font-bold text-md">Contact Us</h2>
			<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at: support@priisma.com</p>
			
			<p>By submitting your Form Data through the Lead Gen Forms, you acknowledge and agree to the terms and conditions set forth in this Privacy Policy.</p>
		</section>
		
		<footer class="py-4 text-slate-700 bg-slate-200">
		  <div class="container px-4 mx-auto">
			<p class="text-sm text-center">&copy; 2023 Priisma — All rights reserved.</p>
		  </div>
		</footer>
	  </body>
</html>
